##### 
NOTE: THE IONS MODEL IMPLEMENTED HERE IS SUPERCEDED BY
THE GENERAL COARSE-GRAINED IONS (GCGI), WHICH IS NOW INCLUDED
WITH USER-3SPN2.
#####


Configuration files were generated with the command;

../../DSIM_ICNF/icnf.exe ../seq 0 1 . 1 ../ions.dat

The bdna_curv.in file also contains the line 

comm_modify mode single cutoff 30.0

which helps prevent segementation faults when 
simulating large systems across many processors.

